### 11.1 Global frame (intended)
- Logged-in experience has a consistent frame:
  - Primary nav
  - Main content
  - Contextual actions on relevant pages (e.g. RG tools)

### 11.2 Navigation by user state (INTENDED ORDER — EDIT THIS)
Active Member nav (proposed order for review):
1) Dashboard
2) Communications
3) Meetings
4) Polls
5) Governance
6) Documents
7) Finance
8) Noticeboard / Calendar
9) Profile

RG/Elected adds:
- RG area
- Pending approvals
- Membership database
- Plot tools
- Actions register
