## 12) Data Model Summary (Schema Targets; no assumptions beyond named entities)

Entities implied/required by your workflows:
- User/Profile
- MembershipCycle (AGM→AGM)
- MemberStatus (active/inactive)
- Plot
- PlotJoinGroup (joined plots group; supports >2 plots)
- PlotPerson (owners/tenants) with active flag
- RGMember + RoleAssignment (Chair/Vice/Secretary/Treasurer)
- TemporaryMode state (derived from RG count < 4)
- Poll
- Vote (with computed weight snapshot)
- GovernanceSetting
- GovernanceChangeLog (old/new/poll/effective time; document link)
- Meeting
- Agenda (draft/approved)
- Minutes (draft/approved)
- AgendaSubmission (member submitted)
- ActionItem (linked to poll/meeting/minutes/communication)
- CommunicationThread
- CommunicationUpdate + Attachments
- DocumentFolder
- Document + Archive metadata
- FinanceEntry/FinanceReport
- AnnualReport

