## 13) Implementation “Where We Are” (Use as checklist)

### 13.1 UI
- [ ] Navigation matches section 11 exactly
- [ ] Active vs inactive gating enforced
- [ ] RG vs elected-RG gating enforced
- [ ] Pages match workflows (polls, meetings, communications, docs, finance)

### 13.2 Governance workflows
- [ ] Suggest poll → pending approvals → activate with 4 RG → vote → close → archive
- [ ] Governance change auto-applies and logs + archives

### 13.3 Meetings workflows
- [ ] Create meeting → auto draft docs → approval → visible to members
- [ ] Agenda submission form → RG approval → add to agenda

### 13.4 Membership DB / plot tools
- [ ] Membership database visible only to elected-RG
- [ ] Profile deletion = user details removed; plot persists as unregistered
- [ ] Plot owner reassignment logged; requires external confirmation

### 13.5 Archive policy
- [ ] No hard deletes for governance records
- [ ] Archived items read-only except where 4 RG approvals allow change

